# Internal business / commercial planning documents.
# All business, legal, partner, pricing, runbook, and sales-kit documents
# live in /business and are never committed to this repo. This protects
# confidential commercial information from accidental leak via code escrow,
# repo sharing with junior developers, or public mirroring.
